se of zalcitabine with other drugs that have the potential to cause peripheral neuropathy should be avoided whenever possible.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/47308/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Valaciclovir, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Acyclovir, Brincidofovir, Elbasvir, Famciclovir, Doravirine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
